WHERE AM I?

2
00:00:31,750 --> 00:00:35,583
"THE RIVER STYX"?
THAT DOESN'T SOUND LIKE FUN.

3
00:00:35,666 --> 00:00:38,875
- COME ON, AKIHISA.
COME TO OUR SIDE OF THE RIVER.

4
00:00:38,958 --> 00:00:42,208
- IT'S NICER THAN IT LOOKS.
I PROMISE.

5
00:00:42,291 --> 00:00:44,916
- EVERYTHING IS
BETTER OVER HERE.

6
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,916
- TRUST ME, THERE'S NO REASON
FOR YOU TO BE SCARED, MAN.

7
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,875
THIS SIDE JUST TAKES
A LITTLE GETTING USED TO.

8
00:00:49,958 --> 00:00:51,666
NO BIG DEAL.
- YUUJI?

9
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:53,083
WHAT THE HELL ARE
YOU DOING OVER THERE?

10
00:00:53,166 --> 00:00:55,000
- I'M HERE BECAUSE I'M HERE.

11
00:00:55,083 --> 00:00:56,666
IT'S ALL GOOD.
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.

12
00:00:56,750 --> 00:00:59,333
THERE'S NO REASON FOR YOU
TO BE SCARED, I PROMISE.

13
00:00:59,416 --> 00:01:03,125
COME ON OVER.  DON'T BE AFRAID.
EVERYTHING IS FINE.

14
00:01:03,208 --> 00:01:04,625
- ( screams )

15
00:01:08,875 --> 00:01:11,125
- ( singing in Japanese )

16
00:02:36,125 --> 00:02:37,458
- ( shivers )

17
00:02:42,250 --> 00:02:45,958
- HEY, WHERE ARE WE?
- I DON'T REMEMBER EXACTLY.

18
00:02:46,041 --> 00:02:48,083
BUT I FEEL LIKE WE WENT
THROUGH HELL TO GET HERE.

19
00:02:48,166 --> 00:02:49,666
- YOU HAD TO KNOW
THE GIRLS WOULD FIND OUT

20
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,458
WHAT YOU WERE UP TO.
I MEAN, IF YOU ASK ME,

21
00:02:51,541 --> 00:02:52,458
YOU GUYS ARE LUCKY
TO BE BREATHING.

22
00:02:52,541 --> 00:02:53,958
- YOU'RE RIGHT.

23
00:02:54,041 --> 00:02:55,833
WE SHOULD BE
GONERS FOR SURE.

24
00:02:57,875 --> 00:03:00,041
- Fukuhara: AKIHISA AND YUUJI
MADE A CONTEST

25
00:03:00,125 --> 00:03:02,041
OUT OF HITTING ON
CHICKS YESTERDAY.

26
00:03:02,125 --> 00:03:04,750
THE GIRLS FOUND OUT AND
PUNISHED THEM SOMEWHAT SEVERELY.

27
00:03:04,833 --> 00:03:06,250
- I'VE NEVER SEEN
SOMEONE PUNISHED

28
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:07,875
AS GRUESOMELY AS YOU WERE.

29
00:03:07,958 --> 00:03:09,500
I CAN HARDLY BEAR 
TO THINK ABOUT IT.

30
00:03:09,583 --> 00:03:11,375
IT WAS JUST SO
HORRIBLY SADISTIC.

31
00:03:11,458 --> 00:03:13,750
- YEAH, I'M GLAD
I CAN'T REMEMBER IT.

32
00:03:13,833 --> 00:03:16,208
- ME TOO, ALTHOUGH I GUESS
WE DESERVED WHATEVER IT WAS.

33
00:03:16,291 --> 00:03:17,875
WE WERE BEING JERKS.
- I'M JUST SAYING,

34
00:03:17,958 --> 00:03:19,583
THE NEXT TIME
YOU'RE WITH GIRLS,

35
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:21,708
YOU SHOULD PROBABLY AVOID
FLIRTING WITH OTHER GIRLS.

36
00:03:21,791 --> 00:03:24,000
- YOU KNOW, NOW THAT
YOU MENTION IT,

37
00:03:24,083 --> 00:03:25,458
WE MIGHT HAVE GOTTEN OFF
A LITTLE EASY.

38
00:03:25,541 --> 00:03:27,083
- I DON'T KNOW
IF I'D EXACTLY CALL

39
00:03:27,166 --> 00:03:29,166
A NEAR-DEATH EXPERIENCE
"GETTING OFF EASY."

40
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:30,958
- NO, I WOULDN'T EITHER,
BUT I THINK I GET

41
00:03:31,041 --> 00:03:32,375
WHERE AKI'S COMING FROM.

42
00:03:32,458 --> 00:03:34,125
THERE MIGHT BE MORE
PUNISHMENT TO COME.

43
00:03:34,208 --> 00:03:35,750
- SO WHAT DO YOU
THINK WE SHOULD DO? RUN?

44
00:03:35,833 --> 00:03:36,958
- Minami: SOMEONE SAY "RUN"?

45
00:03:39,333 --> 00:03:41,041
- WE'RE TOO LATE.

46
00:03:44,833 --> 00:03:46,375
- Girls: TA DA!

47
00:03:49,708 --> 00:03:52,875
- HEY, GIRLS.  YOU LOOK NICE,
BUT WHY ARE YOU WEARING YUKATA?

48
00:03:52,958 --> 00:03:55,875
- BECAUSE THEY'RE HOLDING 
A FESTIVAL IN TOWN, SILLY.

49
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:01,208
- SO, AKIHISA,
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

50
00:04:01,291 --> 00:04:03,583
- UM, THEY'RE GOOD.
YOU GUYS LOOK SO NICE.

51
00:04:03,666 --> 00:04:06,291
- REALLY? THIS IS KINDA
MY FIRST TIME WEARING ONE.

52
00:04:06,375 --> 00:04:08,208
- OH, YEAH, YOU
GREW UP IN GERMANY.

53
00:04:08,291 --> 00:04:09,708
I DON'T KNOW WHY
I KEEP FORGETTING THAT.

54
00:04:15,208 --> 00:04:16,666
- WHAT? WILL YOU QUIT STARING?

55
00:04:18,791 --> 00:04:20,250
- ( gasps ) OH.

56
00:04:20,333 --> 00:04:22,291
I WAS JUST ZONING OUT.
- OR MAYBE

57
00:04:22,375 --> 00:04:24,166
YOU JUST COULDN'T
KEEP YOUR EYES OFF HER.

58
00:04:24,250 --> 00:04:26,083
MINAMI SURE DOES
LOOK PRETTY, DOESN'T SHE?

59
00:04:26,166 --> 00:04:27,791
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

60
00:04:27,875 --> 00:04:30,166
- KIMONOS ARE SUPER GREAT
BECAUSE THEY MAKE YOU LOOK GOOD

61
00:04:30,250 --> 00:04:31,958
EVEN IF YOU'VE
GOT SMALL BOOBS.

62
00:04:32,041 --> 00:04:34,125
- I STILL DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

63
00:04:34,208 --> 00:04:37,416
- OH, WELL, THEN I SUPPOSE
I BETTER SHOW YOU, HUH?

64
00:04:37,500 --> 00:04:39,458
PAY ATTENTION.
( kisses )

65
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:43,791
UH-OH.
- HMM? ( screams )

66
00:04:43,875 --> 00:04:45,083
- YOU SEE WHAT I MEAN?

67
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:46,416
HE LOST IT WAY FASTER
THAN USUAL.

68
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:48,166
- ( gasps )

69
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:50,333
- LISTEN, KOUTA,
YOU'RE GONNA BE JUST FINE.

70
00:04:50,416 --> 00:04:52,791
STAY WITH ME NOW.
- ( groans )

71
00:04:52,875 --> 00:04:55,833
I KNOW.  IT LOOKS
A LOT WORSE THAN IT IS.

72
00:04:55,916 --> 00:04:57,666
SO DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

73
00:05:00,041 --> 00:05:01,458
- YUUJI.

74
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,333
HOW DO YOU LIKE MY YUKATA?
TELL THE TRUTH.

75
00:05:05,416 --> 00:05:07,791
- IT'S FINE AND I ALWAYS
TELL THE TRUTH, DON'T I?

76
00:05:07,875 --> 00:05:10,291
- THANK YOU.
IN THAT CASE THEN,

77
00:05:10,375 --> 00:05:11,958
WOULD YOU LIKE 
TO GET MARRIED?

78
00:05:12,041 --> 00:05:14,541
- NO FREAKING WAY.
- ALL RIGHT, THAN WOULD YOU

79
00:05:14,625 --> 00:05:16,583
RATHER MOVE FORWARD
BY GETTING ENGAGED FIRST?

80
00:05:16,666 --> 00:05:19,416
- NOT EVEN A LITTLE.
- THEN LET ME ASK YOU THIS.

81
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:21,333
- NO MEANS NO.

82
00:05:21,416 --> 00:05:22,833
- WOULD YOU LIKE
TO KEEP BREATHING?

83
00:05:22,916 --> 00:05:24,083
- YEAH, OKAY FINE!

84
00:05:24,166 --> 00:05:25,708
YOU LOOK GREAT, SHOUKO.
VERY PRETTY.

85
00:05:25,791 --> 00:05:29,333
- THAT'S SO SWEET
OF YOU TO SAY, YUUJI.

86
00:05:29,416 --> 00:05:30,916
- LIKE YOU GAVE ME A CHOICE.

87
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,583
- MY MOTHER ALWAYS TOLD ME
TO DO WHATEVER IT TAKES

88
00:05:33,666 --> 00:05:34,791
TO KEEP MY MAN.

89
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:41,083
- THIS IS WEIRD. I THOUGHT
THEY WERE ALL MAD AT US.

90
00:05:41,166 --> 00:05:44,041
I DON'T TRUST THIS,
LIKE NOT AT ALL.

91
00:05:45,708 --> 00:05:47,625
- OKAY, EVERYONE.
ARE WE ALL SET?

92
00:05:47,708 --> 00:05:49,833
IT'S TIME FOR US TO HEAD 
OVER TO THE FESTIVAL NOW.

93
00:05:52,041 --> 00:05:53,916
- AKIRA'S RIGHT.
LET'S GO GUYS.

94
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:56,916
HURRY UP, WE DON'T WANT
TO BE LATE, DO WE?

95
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,916
- I'M SO EXCITED RIGHT NOW.

96
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,416
THIS IS ONLY THE SECOND JAPANESE
FESTIVAL I'VE BEEN TO.

97
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:02,833
- I DON'T WANT
TO MISS ANY OF IT.

98
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:05,875
- GET A MOVE ON, BOYS.

99
00:06:05,958 --> 00:06:08,250
- Both: YEAH, OKAY.

100
00:06:12,375 --> 00:06:14,833
- WOW, EVERYTHING
IS SO SPARKLY.

101
00:06:14,916 --> 00:06:16,333
- I KNOW, FOR REAL.
I LOVE IT.

102
00:06:16,416 --> 00:06:18,791
- YUMMY, SOMEONE HAS
DONER KABOBS HERE.

103
00:06:18,875 --> 00:06:21,541
- THEY LOOK GOOD TOO.
- WELL, WE SHOULD TRY THEM.

104
00:06:21,625 --> 00:06:23,250
IF THEY LOOK GOOD,
WHY NOT, RIGHT?

105
00:06:23,333 --> 00:06:25,708
- ( screams )
- YUP, MORE PUNISHMENT.

106
00:06:25,791 --> 00:06:28,125
I WANT YOU TO GO
BUY SOME FOR ME.

107
00:06:28,208 --> 00:06:29,916
- ( screams )

108
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:33,666
- WHY DID I HAVE
TO AGREE WITH HER?

109
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:35,583
- I'M GOING TO ASSUME
YOU WANT SOME TOO.

110
00:06:35,666 --> 00:06:38,250
I DON'T MIND PAYING FOR THEM.
- IT'S FINE.

111
00:06:38,333 --> 00:06:41,375
I WON'T ARGUE WITH YOU.
HOLD ON.  ARE YOU SERIOUS?

112
00:06:41,458 --> 00:06:43,875
YOU'RE GONNA BUY THEM?
- WHAT'S WRONG?

113
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:46,666
DID YOU WANT TO PAY INSTEAD?
- NO, NO, AS YOU WERE.

114
00:06:48,750 --> 00:06:50,500
I WONDER.

115
00:06:50,583 --> 00:06:52,875
MAYBE SHE REALLY
DID FORGIVE ME. 

116
00:06:54,333 --> 00:06:55,750
- HERE IT IS.

117
00:06:55,833 --> 00:06:58,291
I GOT US ONE ORDER TO SPLIT
IF THAT'S OKAY.

118
00:06:58,375 --> 00:07:00,166
THERE ARE A LOT OF THINGS HERE
I WANT TO TRY.

119
00:07:00,250 --> 00:07:01,833
SO I DIDN'T WANT
TO FILL UP TOO SOON.

120
00:07:01,916 --> 00:07:04,333
- YEAH, GOOD PLAN.
I'M TOTALLY COOL WITH THAT.

121
00:07:04,416 --> 00:07:06,500
SO HOW DOES IT TASTE?
- OH, I CAN'T EAT AND WALK.

122
00:07:06,583 --> 00:07:07,541
I'M NOT SURE YET.

123
00:07:09,416 --> 00:07:11,333
I GUESS THEY DON'T
USE LAMB IN JAPAN,

124
00:07:11,416 --> 00:07:13,458
BUT IT'S STILL PRETTY YUMMY.
YOU TRY.

125
00:07:13,541 --> 00:07:15,083
YOU MIGHT ACTUALLY LIKE IT
BETTER THIS WAY.

126
00:07:16,916 --> 00:07:20,041
- OH WOW, THIS IS REALLY GOOD.

127
00:07:20,125 --> 00:07:22,166
- OH, AKI, YOUR FACE.

128
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:24,250
YOU'VE GOT SOME SAUCE ON IT.

129
00:07:26,083 --> 00:07:29,541
- THANKS, THAT WAS NICE
AND AWKWARD.

130
00:07:29,625 --> 00:07:32,708
- AKIHISA, I JUST BOUGHT
SOME OCTOPUS DUMPLINGS. 

131
00:07:32,791 --> 00:07:34,208
WOULD YOU LIKE TO TRY SOME?

132
00:07:34,291 --> 00:07:36,666
- WELL, YEAH, OF COURSE I WOULD.
THANKS, HIMEJI.

133
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:37,666
ONE DUMPLING PLEASE.

134
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:41,375
- HERE YOU GO.
SAY AAH.

135
00:07:41,458 --> 00:07:43,416
WHAT'S WRONG?
I THOUGHT YOU WANTED ONE.

136
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:44,708
DOES IT NOT LOOK GOOD?

137
00:07:44,791 --> 00:07:48,166
- IT LOOKS FINE.
IT'S NOT THAT.

138
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:51,500
- WELL, THEN.  AAH.

139
00:07:51,583 --> 00:07:53,208
- AAH.

140
00:07:53,291 --> 00:07:54,916
MHMM, YUM.

141
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,583
THE PANCAKE PART
IS HOT AND CREAMY

142
00:07:56,666 --> 00:07:58,458
AND THE OCTOPUS
IS NICE AND CHEWY.

143
00:07:58,541 --> 00:08:00,333
( gasps )
NO WAIT, AKIRA!

144
00:08:00,416 --> 00:08:02,250
PLEASE! I KNOW
THAT SOUNDED SEXUAL,

145
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:03,791
BUT IT WASN'T AT ALL.
I SWEAR.

146
00:08:03,875 --> 00:08:06,250
- "THE OCTOPUS IS CHEWY,"
THAT'S SEXUAL?

147
00:08:06,333 --> 00:08:07,791
- IT'S NOT?
- ARE YOU TRYING TO SAY

148
00:08:07,875 --> 00:08:10,041
YOU DIDN'T LIKE IT?
- NO.

149
00:08:10,125 --> 00:08:12,958
- WHAT'D YOU SCREW UP, AKI,
THIS TIME?

150
00:08:13,041 --> 00:08:15,041
QUIT FREAKING OUT.
IT'S JUST A FESTIVAL.

151
00:08:15,125 --> 00:08:16,958
YOU CAN BE SUCH
A BABY SOMETIMES.

152
00:08:17,041 --> 00:08:18,708
- WHO'S FREAKING OUT?
YOU'RE THE ONE

153
00:08:18,791 --> 00:08:19,916
SHELLING OUT
AT EVERY BOOTH.

154
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,333
- HEY, YOU DON'T KNOW.

155
00:08:21,416 --> 00:08:23,125
THESE COULD HAVE BEEN
TOTALLY FREE, GOD.

156
00:08:23,208 --> 00:08:24,916
- THIS IS ONLY YOUR
SECOND FESTIVAL HERE.

157
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,666
IT'S OKAY IF YOU COULDN'T
HELP YOURSELF.

158
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:29,000
- THANK YOU.  COTTON CANDY
IS LIKE WAY DELICIOUS.

159
00:08:29,083 --> 00:08:30,208
DO YOU WANT TO TRY SOME, AKI?

160
00:08:30,291 --> 00:08:31,750
- WHAT?

161
00:08:36,416 --> 00:08:38,666
SURE, I LOVE THAT STUFF.

162
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:41,041
- YEAH, YOU DO.
SAY AHH.

163
00:08:41,125 --> 00:08:43,333
- AAH.
- IT'S GOOD, AM I RIGHT?

164
00:08:43,416 --> 00:08:45,916
- YEAH, IT'S GOOD.
THANKS, MINAMI.

165
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:48,625
- OH, YOU'RE WELCOME.

166
00:08:48,708 --> 00:08:51,375
- YUUJI, WOULD YOU LIKE
SOME OF MY NOODLES?

167
00:08:51,458 --> 00:08:54,000
- YEAH, SURE. I GUESS I'LL
HAVE SOME IF YOU DON'T MIND.

168
00:08:54,083 --> 00:08:55,708
- I HAVE OKONOMIYAKI TOO.

169
00:08:55,791 --> 00:08:57,708
- THANKS, THAT'S 
VERY NICE OF YOU.

170
00:08:57,791 --> 00:08:59,458
- WOULD YOU LIKE SOME SODA?

171
00:08:59,541 --> 00:09:01,250
- YES, MUCH APPRECIATED.

172
00:09:01,333 --> 00:09:04,333
- NICE, YUUJI LOOKS LIKE
HE GOT OFF THE HOOK TOO.

173
00:09:04,416 --> 00:09:05,916
I MEAN, THIS IS A FESTIVAL.

174
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,333
WHY WOULD THEY WANT
TO BE PISSED THE WHOLE TIME?

175
00:09:07,416 --> 00:09:08,708
TODAY ROCKS!

176
00:09:08,791 --> 00:09:11,208
- AKIHISA,
THEY HAVE BABY CHICKENS

177
00:09:11,291 --> 00:09:12,916
IN DIFFERENT COLORS OVER THERE.

178
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,541
THERE'S LIKE GREEN ONES,
AND BLUE ONES, AND EVERYTHING.

179
00:09:15,625 --> 00:09:18,458
- YEAH, THEY JUST HIRE SOMEONE
TO PAINT THE BABIES.

180
00:09:18,541 --> 00:09:20,541
- THAT'S NOT TRUE.
IT'S BECAUSE OF THEIR BREED

181
00:09:20,625 --> 00:09:22,791
OR SOMETHING NATURAL LIKE THAT.
- ( laughs )

182
00:09:22,875 --> 00:09:25,083
YOU TWO ARE LIKE
BEYOND STUPID.

183
00:09:25,166 --> 00:09:26,958
KOUTA, WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT ALL THIS?

184
00:09:31,083 --> 00:09:32,291
- ( screeches )

185
00:09:32,375 --> 00:09:34,250
- ( evil chuckle )

186
00:09:34,333 --> 00:09:36,708
I'LL COLOR YOU 
HOWEVER I LIKE!

187
00:09:36,791 --> 00:09:40,291
- WELL, PAINTING MAKES
A SICK KIND OF SENSE. 

188
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:43,041
- SO TELL ME, AKI, ARE YOU
HAVING A GOOD TIME YET?

189
00:09:43,125 --> 00:09:44,291
- YUP.

190
00:09:44,375 --> 00:09:46,458
- AND, YUUJI, ARE
YOU HAVING FUN?

191
00:09:46,541 --> 00:09:48,208
- YUP, SURE AM.

192
00:09:48,291 --> 00:09:49,916
- HEY, LOOK, AKIHISA.

193
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,291
IT TURNS OUT THE FESTIVAL
IS THROWING A SPECIAL EVENT

194
00:09:52,375 --> 00:09:54,000
LATER ON TODAY.
- "ENTER TO WIN

195
00:09:54,083 --> 00:09:56,541
OUR FIRST EVER SUMMER
MISS YUKATA BEAUTY PAGEANT."

196
00:09:56,625 --> 00:09:58,166
NICE.
- BEAUTY PAGEANT?

197
00:09:58,250 --> 00:09:59,708
- WE SHOULD TOTALLY
GO WATCH THAT.

198
00:09:59,791 --> 00:10:01,541
- MY CAMERA AND I
ARE UP FOR IT.

199
00:10:01,625 --> 00:10:03,291
- ALL RIGHTY THEN.
HOW ABOUT WE ALL GO.

200
00:10:03,375 --> 00:10:04,625
- BETTER YET,
WHY DON'T WE HAVE EVERYONE

201
00:10:04,708 --> 00:10:05,583
JUST COMPETE IN THE THING.

202
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:10,125
WELL, I MEAN, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO OBVIOUSLY.

203
00:10:10,208 --> 00:10:12,166
BUT I JUST THOUGHT
IT'D BE A NICE MEMORY

204
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:14,958
OF THE DAY AND STUFF.
THAT'S ALL.

205
00:10:15,041 --> 00:10:17,333
- GREAT IDEA.
- WHAT? REALLY?

206
00:10:17,416 --> 00:10:19,583
- YES, OF COURSE, WE SHOULD
ALL DO THIS TOGETHER.

207
00:10:19,666 --> 00:10:22,500
- SOMETHING WE ARE SURE
TO NEVER FORGET.

208
00:10:22,583 --> 00:10:25,625
- ALL RIGHT, LET'S
COMPETE IN THE PAGEANT.

209
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:28,083
LET'S HAVE
EVERYONE HERE COMPETE.

210
00:10:28,166 --> 00:10:29,750
- Both: RUN!

211
00:10:35,375 --> 00:10:38,416
- ( screams )

212
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:40,833
- WHERE ARE YOU OFF TO
IN SUCH A HURRY? YOU SCARED?

213
00:10:40,916 --> 00:10:43,250
- WE'RE GOING TO PARTICIPATE
IN THE BEAUTY PAGEANT.

214
00:10:43,333 --> 00:10:44,375
ISN'T THAT RIGHT, YUUJI?

215
00:10:44,458 --> 00:10:45,916
- WHAT? DON'T TAKE
THIS PERSONALLY,

216
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,208
BUT YOU GUYS AREN'T
MAKING ANY SENSE LIKE AT ALL.

217
00:10:48,291 --> 00:10:51,000
- FOR REAL.
WHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON?

218
00:10:51,083 --> 00:10:53,875
- HITTING ON GIRLS EARLIER.
- SURELY YOU DIDN'T BELIEVE

219
00:10:53,958 --> 00:10:55,583
WE WERE FINISHED
WITH YOU BOYS YET.

220
00:10:55,666 --> 00:10:57,375
- YOU SHOULD KNOW BY NOW
THAT WE WOULD MAKE YOU PAY

221
